HEADWORD: Unmistakable
<hw>Un`mis*tak"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Incapable of
being mistaken or misunderstood; clear; plain; obvious; evident.</def>
-- <wordforms><wf>Un`mis*tak"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

